ion-attachment-3502023" class="wp-caption-text"> 《博德之门 3》图片来源：Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p>由于她的心脏被地狱引擎取代，卡拉赫正在慢慢死去。尽管如此，她仍然富有同情心、幽默风趣，并为那些需要帮助或处境不利的人提供强烈的保护。</p><p>另一方面，阿斯塔里奥一开始就具有操纵性和自私性，对于坚持良好阵营的玩家来说很难让他喜欢自己的角色。然而，据透露，他原本是一位吸血鬼领主的奴隶，吸血鬼领主想要杀死他来提升。</p><p> Karlach、Astarion 和<em>《博德之门 3》</em>的其他角色是<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/baldurs-gate-3-review-3481761"><em>NME</em>游戏五星级评论</a>中的众多亮点之一，现在 Béart 和 Newbon 分享了让他们想起自己角色的歌曲播放列表。</p><p>在<a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/4SANjT7whL2t6YsSxiAGQn?si=160607027f6c4a84&amp;nd=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Karlach 的播放列表</a>中，摇滚贯穿始终，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jay-z">Jay-Z</a>的《Crazy In Love》、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bjork">比约克</a>的《Army Of Me》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardi-b">Cardi B</a>的《Bodak Yellow》和卡罗尔·金的《You&#39;ve》 Got A Friend 穿插了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nine-inch-nails">九寸钉</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/motorhead">Motörhead</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">Led Zeppelin</a>的经典曲目。 </p><figure id="attachment_3478283" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3478283" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3478283" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/